A resident was getting his car washed when he noticed a vagrant being chased from the premises on Sunday afternoon. He said he did not know whether the vagrant was being chased by the owner of the premises or a caretaker. “A while later, a group of vagrants came up the road and sat nearby. After the man who chased the vagrant away left, they stole the gate,” he said. He said the vagrants did not hide when a police van drove past. To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
